<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>FCIT Event Finder respects your privacy. This page explains what information we collect, why we collect it, and how you can control it.</p>

<h2>Information we collect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Information you provide:</strong> When you use forms on this site (for example the Contact form or when creating events if authenticated), you may provide personal information such as name, email address, and message content.</li>
    <li><strong>Automatic data:</strong> We may collect non-personal information automatically, such as pages visited, browser type, and IP address for diagnostics and to improve the site.</li>
</ul>

<h2>How we use information</h2>
<ul>
    <li>To respond to inquiries and provide requested functionality.</li>
    <li>To maintain and improve the website and to analyze usage patterns.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations if required.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Cookies</h2>
<p>We use cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, but some features of the site may not work correctly if cookies are disabled.</p>

<h2>Third-party services</h2>
<p>We may use third-party services (for example analytics providers). Those services have their own privacy policies — please review them separately.</p>

<h2>Security</h2>
<p>We take reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect information. However, no method of transmission over the internet is completely secure.</p>

<h2>Your choices</h2>
<p>You can contact us to request removal or correction of personal data we hold about you. To contact us, use the <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Contact">Contact</a> page or email <a href="mailto:aalsebaee0002@stu.kau.edu.sa">aalsebaee0002@stu.kau.edu.sa</a>.</p>

<h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
<p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The "Last updated" date below indicates when this page was last changed.</p>

